    <footnotes>
        <footnote id="F1">On November 7, 2018, the reporting person contributed 32,000 shares of M&amp;T Bank Corporation common stock to a Grantor Retained Annuity Trust (&quot;GRAT #1&quot;) of which the reporting person is the trustee and his descendants are beneficiaries.  The reporting person continues to report the beneficial ownership of all of the M&amp;T Bank Corporation common stock held by the GRAT #1 but disclaims beneficial ownership except to the extent of his pecuniary interest therein.</footnote>
